	('b0e18eb2-463f-4b8e-9607-fa6372d2a86f', 'reading', 6, 'What should team members bring to the meeting?', 'reports', 'food', 'drinks', 'friends', NULL, 'A', 2, '團隊成員應攜帶報告，以分享他們的項目進度。', '2025-09-23 10:00:25.000000', '2025-09-23 10:00:25.000000', 'vocab', NULL, '01f3c23f-41e9-4a8e-98ff-d64e8ff319f4', NULL),
	('52ac63e2-4066-4cdd-bd54-fa805919a52e', 'listen', 2, 'What is the main benefit of having health insurance?', 'It helps cover medical expenses.', 'It provides discounts on groceries.', 'It offers free gym memberships.', NULL, NULL, 'A', 3, '這道題目測試對於保健相關詞彙的理解。選項A正確，因為醫療保險的主要功能是幫助支付醫療費用，而其他選項與主題無關。', '2025-09-24 00:30:09.000000', '2025-09-24 00:30:09.000000', 'vocab', '9b54918e-f9c6-4809-b9a0-18d436009e36', NULL, NULL),
	('83934c58-44c0-49d3-b586-fa8b574f060d', 'listen', 2, 'What does the company need to focus on for the new project?', 'We should improve our marketing strategies.', 'I think we need more engineers for development.', 'Yes, the design needs some adjustments.', NULL, NULL, 'B', 3, '本題考查對於公司新計劃的重點，選項 B 提到需要增加工程師以支持產品開發，符合問題要求；選項 A 和 C 雖然合理，但並無明確聚焦於開發需求。', '2025-09-16 16:20:56.000000', '2025-09-16 16:20:56.000000', 'pos', 'a19ef3f9-6327-4d3b-99fb-6561251463be', NULL, NULL),
	('77da7671-2293-45d7-a0c7-fab7a829170a', 'reading', 6, 'Our team will be exploring advanced technologies that __1.__ improve our current offerings.', 'quickly', 'rarely', 'slightly', 'significantly', NULL, 'D', 2, '此空白處需填入副詞修飾動詞 improve，最合適的選擇是 significantly，意為"顯著地"，符合上下文的期待。', '2025-09-22 07:00:25.000000', '2025-09-22 07:00:25.000000', 'vocab', NULL, 'a02ca828-e109-4501-887a-a0aae654eaa3', NULL),
